              <li><p>Vector Operations and Applications</p></li>
              <li><p>Equations of Lines, Planes, and Surfaces</p></li>
              <li><p>Vector Functions</p></li>
              <li><p>Functions of Two Variables</p></li>
            </ul></p></introduction>
